data.description: Ask about this home's assumable FHA loan at 3.125%.  Discover lake living in this 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom gem nestled within the coveted Heritage Ranch gated community. This 3bd, 2ba home has an open floor plan, vaulted ceilings, central heat & air, dual pane windows, indoor laundry and an oversized garage-like carport including storage shed.  The master bedroom is on the other side of the home from the other 2 bedrooms adding privacy.  Entertain or unwind on the comfortable back patio and yard.  Heritage Ranch offers not just a home but a lifestyle, with exclusive access to a private launch ramp, swimming pools, baseball diamond, playgrounds, as well as walking, hiking and biking trails. Take the opportunity to call this haven yours and embrace the Heritage Ranch experience. Welcome home!
